data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! This wonderful home is located in the highly sought after and well established neighborhood of Devonshire. With over 2700 square feet this one has so much to offer. Walking through the front doors you are greeted by beautiful LVP floors that are resilient and cover all of the first floor. Once you enter there is an oversized office directly the right of the front door along with a half bath. The family room opens up to a large kitchen that is a chefs dream. The primary bedroom is located on the first floor and is a great place to unwind after a long day. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms, a game room which can serve as an additional living area and a full bath. Being that this home was built in 2021 and very well kept is like new. With the Devonshire HOA it gives the owners access to 4 ponds that can be fished, 2 pools, a splash pad, sand volleyball pit, a basketball court and a huge jogging or walking trail.
